Poynting has launched the OMNI-280 antenna, which is aimed at Point of Sale (POS) systems, M2M applications, and the Internet of Things (IoT). The OMNI-280 is a high-performance indoor and outdoor antenna, which provide users with an affordable solution for poor signal strength. It is a medium-gain OMNI and general-purpose antenna, providing frequency band coverage at 698MHz to 3,800MHz. The OMNI-280 antenna features: Poynting CEO Michael Howard said the design of the OMNI-280 addresses applications in smart buildings that incorporate climate control, access control, security, and irrigation. It can be also be applied to smart power metering, and gas and water metering.